node.text:
Spotting sea snakes with @brodiemoss 😳Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your content in our account: @explorerfervor 

“Sea snakes normally avoid humans but this time of year they become very active, sexually frustrated and potentially aggressive as they search for a mate 🐍 like this old fella who appeared from the ocean floor and followed me around on my paddle board before disappearing 😅”

What would you do in this situation? 😱

📽 @brodiemoss
📍Australia

Stella Island Resort in Crete, Greece is a dream 😍 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your content in our account: @explorerfervor 

What do you think? Which photo/video is your favorite? ✨💙🇬🇷

📷 @karpathakis.experience 
📍Stella Island Resort, Crete, Greece

Sunsets in Santorini 🌅 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting explorerfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @explorerfervor 

Tag a friend who you’d escape to Greece with!

Loved for its one of a kind architecture and beach views, this Greek town will take your breath away. If you’re visiting Santorini this summer, don’t forget to hike to the town’s volcano and unwind at a winery afterwards ☀️🍷

📷 @cbezerraphotos & @_letstravel_
📍 Santorini, Greece
